@startuml
actor User
participant MapPage
participant LocationService
participant GeofenceService
participant EventGate as "GeofenceEventGate"
participant NarrationManager
participant API as "MapApi"
database DB

User -> MapPage: Open map
MapPage -> API: GET /api/v1/sync/version
API -> DB: Query latest POI version
DB --> API: version
API --> MapPage: version

MapPage -> API: GET /api/v1/pois
API -> DB: Query active POIs
DB --> API: POI list
API --> MapPage: POI list

MapPage -> GeofenceService: RegisterAsync(pois)
MapPage -> LocationService: StartTracking()

LocationService --> MapPage: New location(lat,lng)
GeofenceService --> MapPage: OnPoiEvent(poi, ENTER/NEAR)
MapPage -> EventGate: ShouldAccept(poi,event)

alt accepted
  MapPage -> API: GET /api/v1/pois/{id}/narration
  API -> DB: Load narration by lang+event
  DB --> API: narration text
  API --> MapPage: narration payload

  MapPage -> NarrationManager: HandleAsync(announcement, text)
  NarrationManager -> NarrationManager: Enqueue + worker process
  NarrationManager --> MapPage: playback completed

  MapPage -> API: POST /api/v1/analytics/visit
  MapPage -> API: POST /api/v1/analytics/listen-duration
else rejected
  MapPage --> MapPage: Ignore duplicate/spam event
end

@enduml
